Titolo: Freedom Wars

Anno: 2014

Descrizione: Freedom Wars (フリーダムウォーズ, Furīdamuwōzu) is a Japanese action role-playing video game developed by Japan Studio for the PlayStation Vita. Released in 2014 and set in the distant future where the majority of humankind is imprisoned in penal city-states known as Panopticons which wage war against one another, the game involves players cooperating to fight enemies and contribute towards their Panopticon. The game was one of most successful first-party PlayStation Vita titles in Japan, achieving the second highest all-time opening sales for Vita software sold there.

Genere: Action role-playing 

Valutazione: 73
